{"tid":1387489,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"武運長久 七生報國","createTime":"2019-07-30T14:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:39:36.000Z","uid":3302,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d04f77ab292e56604263a94e15a9bc5898d4da7f","tid":1387489,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJ3wMYe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJ3wMYe.gif&h=d2121e89&s={SIZE}\" /> <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B7%BA%E6%B2%BC%E7%A8%BB%E6%AC%A1%E9%83%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E6%25B7%25BA%25E6%25B2%25BC%25E7%25A8%25BB%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%2583%258E&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNryOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=558b7ac9\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E6%B7%BA%E6%B2%BC%E7%A8%BB%E6%AC%A1%E9%83%8E</a></blockquote><br />\n各位再見"},{"pid":"365b1f4262dc85b65a3e2e9110c585ef275214ba","tid":1387489,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"喂喂 冷靜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600120227dbd21e42f2d70e04e7ea7973018514","tid":1387489,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:21:43.000Z","msg":"1959年，在日本和美國都認為中華民國是代表中國的合法政府的時候，淺沼稻次郎訪問了中國共產黨統治下的中國大陸，並在講話中表示「美帝國主義是日中兩國的共同敵人」[2]。訪華結束後，淺沼稻次郎身著中山裝回到日本，受到了來自右翼勢力以及社會輿論的諸多批判，甚至連黨內的曾禰益等人亦表示無法認同其態度。作出這一發言的動機被認為是對日本曾經的侵略政策及其自身在戰時積極參與政治活動的懺悔。"},{"pid":"53154711228a7f1b1d7269ec60a25f6bf7409353","tid":1387489,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"汝、浅沼稲次郎は日本赤化をはかっている。自分は、汝個人に恨みはないが、社会党の指導的立場にいる者としての責任と、訪中に際しての暴言と、国会乱入の直接のせん動者としての責任からして、汝を許しておくことはできない。ここに於て我、汝に対し天誅を下す。 皇紀二千六百二十年十月十二日 山口二矢。<br />\n（中文翻譯：你，淺沼稻次郎，企圖赤化日本。我和你沒有私仇，但你作為社會黨的領導者，訪問中國時發表惡語，以及在議會中的暴行，讓我無法忍受。我要替天行道消滅你。皇紀二千六百二十年十月十二日 山口二矢）"},{"pid":"fcc706cb69086916f7df2c99b4dc3f28fcc48cf5","tid":1387489,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"數日後，山口二矢在少年監管所中的牆上用牙膏寫下「七生報国 天皇陛下万才」（七生報國，天皇陛下萬歲），上吊自殺，得年僅17歲。"},{"pid":"cd4f9eccfb7ec20e5563365d413d82f8879bb66d","tid":1387489,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:36:48.000Z","msg":"8月5 全香港 齊罷工"},{"pid":"fed5f254cbe5097f9a22c6441182a1986a27644c","tid":1387489,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a00270e6cc489b56fd2b1402b0a14af1234d62","tid":1387489,"uid":229411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T18:57:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ca36ac85e6c579fa41c127207413ba369d41a3","tid":1387489,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"365b1f4262dc85b65a3e2e9110c585ef275214ba","tid":1387489,"uid":9962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:16:20.000Z","msg":"喂喂 冷靜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:39:36.000Z","msg":"香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}